						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Food-safety/Related-developments/Global-project-launched-to-tackle-invasive-pests-of-tomato-and-other-fruits" title="Global project launched to tackle invasive pests of tomato and other fruits" alt="link">Global project launched to tackle invasive pests of tomato and other fruits</a></h2>

	
					<p>A new project has been launched to promote the development of Integrated Pest Management (IPM) practices for the sustainable control of the leaf miner <i>Tuta absoluta</i> and the spotted wing fly <i>Drosophila suzukii</i>, invasive pests of tomato and fruit crops respectively. Called Ameliorating the Sustainable Control of Invasive Insects (ASCII) ENDURE initiated and supported the project through its mobility programme and cooperation with partners outside Europe initiatives.(<a href="http://www.endure-network.eu//about_endure/all_the_news/global_project_launched_to_tackle_invasive_pests" target="_blank">ENDURE</a>, 03/06/2013)</p>
							<p><span class="date">27/06/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Food-safety/Related-developments/Global-project-launched-to-tackle-invasive-pests-of-tomato-and-other-fruits">Read more...</a>
