<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Food-safety/Related-developments/New-avenues-for-the-integrated-management-of-the-palm-moth" title="New avenues for the integrated management of the palm moth" alt="link">New avenues for the integrated management of the palm moth</a></h2>

	
					<p>Researchers found the existence of a sexual pheromone emitted by male <i>Paysandisia archon. </i><i>The</i> discovery opens up new prospects for integrated management of the pest.<a href="http://www.cirad.fr/en/news/all-news-items/press-releases/2013/the-key-to-seduction-for-the-palm-moth-paysandisia-archon" target="_self">http://www.cirad.fr/en/news/all-news-items/press-releases/2013/the-key-to-seduction-for-the-palm-moth-paysandisia-archon</a>(CIRAD, 27/03/2013)</p>
